## Photo Credits

Hero photography by [Annie Spratt](https://unsplash.com/@anniespratt) via [Unsplash](https://unsplash.com).

## Developers

This site was designed and built by fellow Strong resident Aster Haven. With over 15 years web development experience, she enjoys volunteer work supporting her various communities.

[Github](https://github.com/therebelrobot) ⋅ [Portfolio](https://aster.hn)

## Technology

This website is built with [Astro](https://astro.build), [Tailwind CSS](https://tailwindcss.com), and [React](https://react.dev).

Icons provided by [react-icons](https://react-icons.github.io/react-icons/).

Content management powered by [Github](https://github.com) and [Keystatic](https://keystatic.com).
